front.title: •I've Decided To Go Back
front.gametext: USED: During your move phase, take one of your characters with politics at Galactic Senate into hand.  LOST: If you have a Republic character with politics in battle at a site, add one battle destiny; that character is power and politics = 0 until end of turn.
front.lore: 'This is your arena. I feel I must return to mine.'

combo: Queen Amidala, Ruler of Naboo + I've Decided To Go Back (Lost) Two battle destinies for 3 Force!
Queen, Amidala, Ruler of Naboo + I've Decided To Go Back (Used) + Plea To The Court Canceling a Force drain and causing your opponent to miss critical weapon shots.
